Project ns2d: Navier-Stokes TAYLOR-GREEN vortex solution TESTS
==============================================================
The EXACT solution on [0,Pi]x[0,Pi] is known as

DefVar  RhoWater; RhoWater=1000; { kg/m3 WATER MASS Density }
DefVar  nu;       nu=8.9E-4;    { WATER VISCOSITY in Pa.s cf wikipedia}

{The Taylor-Green Vortex Solution 2d Cf. wikipedia}
DefFunc F(t); F=exp(- 2 * nu * t);  EndFunc;
DefFunc XVelocity(t,x,y); XVelocity= sin(x)*cos(y)*F(t); EndFunc;
DefFunc YVelocity(t,x,y); YVelocity=-cos(x)*sin(y)*F(t); EndFunc;
DefFunc Pressure (t,x,y); 
   Pressure=RhoWater*(cos(2*x)+cos(2*y))*(F(t)**2)/4;
EndFunc;

